    & The aim of this wiki is to build a form of {(bold "personal assistant")} to help with the management of a vast repository of {(bold "recorded statistics")} which presently includes {(len (database:select "horaire"))} daily logs, recorded on {(len (keys (database:select "lexicon")))} projects, spanning over {(len (keys database:index))} topics.
