FEU
  UNDE : Neon hermetism
  BREF : The {(link)} era is known as the era of time which began at the {(bold "End Of Science")}.
  BODY
    & From the moment {(link "Actors" "Teleogic Constructors")} began altering the {(link "Soies" "Courses of Time")} and will events into happening, traditional rational intelligence and curiosity were then seen as no more than crafts, or relics of a older time.
    & As per {(bold "Neon Hermetism")}, the whole dimensionality of Time is of a finished shape; accessible and {(link "Soies" "traversible")}. It is hypothetized that the universe is an operating function, rendering a final organization of space via the {(link "Ehrivevnv")}. In order words, the universe exists to formulate a being which is to enter the celestial puzzle, and to emerge as the resulting value.
ACTORS
  UNDE : Neon hermetism
  BREF : The {(link)} are beings {(bold "unaffected by determinism")}, that have {(ital "free will")}.
  BODY
    & Their name "{(ital "actor")}" comes from their ability to actually {(bold "act")}, outside of the will of {(link "mirrors" "determinism")}.
    & Natural Actors, or anomalies, were found to have existed before the {(link "Feu")}, but the True Age of Actors came about with the synthesis of the first Actor by {(link "Neonev")} and the Immigrants.
    & The first synthesized {(link "Actors" "actor")} was tasked to position itself into the {(link "Longest End")}, meaning that it would effectively take control of all things, and of all of time, to steer the sequence of events allowing itself to exist within the {(link "Longest End" "longest lasting possible timeline")} of the computing occurrence.
    & Actors have no names, and their number is unknown, it is possible that multiple actors, or multiple instances of the same actor, are competing for the {(link "Soies" "Longest End")}.
EHRIVEVNV
  UNDE : Neon hermetism
  BREF : The {(link)} is a {(bold "dimensional puzzle")}.
  ICON : M60,150 L60,150 L240,150 M60,240 A90,-90 0 0,0 150,150 A90,90 0 0,0 240,240 M150,60 L150,60 L150,120
  BODY
    & It presenting itself as a {(bold "synthetic celestial structure")}, around which {(link "Dinaisth")} orbits.
    & The Ehrivevnv was found to exists in the timelines that persisted until the End of Time(see {(link "Feu")}). This particularity has brough many forms of life to congregate onto {(link "Dinaisth")} to study it, and has given it its classification of puzzle.
    & The puzzle is orbited by both {(link "Dinaisth")}, and {(link "Aitasla")}. Its discovery, and the research that it inspired, ultimately brought about the {(link "Feu" "completion of Science")}.
    & This superstructure is located further than natural light could ever reach, blanketed in perpetual darkness and cold, in near infinite space and {(link "Vetetrandes" "stasized time")}. The only light ever to reach the surface of the puzzle is emited from {(link "Dinaisth")}.
    & It is believed by {(link "Neon Hermetism")} that it might be the creation of {(link "Actors")} — {(link "Soies Injection")}.
    @ Et haec revelantur in virtute et veritate non Vi.
SOIES
  UNDE : Neon hermetism
  BREF : The {(link)} are the {(bold "studies of the influence of Actors")}.
  ICON : M60,150 L60,150 L240,150 M60,240 A90,-90 0 0,0 150,150 A90,90 0 0,0 240,240 M150,60 L150,60 L150,120
  BODY
    & The {(link "Soies Machine" "Soies machines")} finds their own location according to the {(link "Longest End")}, by generating the value disallowed to exist withinin the currently renderer occuring.
    & It allows for the study of unexisting events, to align the Occuring with the neighboring optimal possible worlds.
    & In other words, by generating the first events outside of the renderable, or Possible World, the {(link "Actors")} steer themselves inside and outside of the possible and impossible chain of events, granting themselves access to various normaly impossible actions.
    > <center><img src='media/identity/soies.png'/></center>
    & This line of research is tied to the discovery of the {(link "Ehrivevnv")} as the resolve of the puzzle only exists within the {(link "Longest End")}.
    λ (join host:children)
LONGEST END
  UNDE : Soies
  BREF : The {(link)} is the succeeding occurence.
  BODY
    & The {(bold "Longest End")} is the longest surviving occurrence amongst the inifities of other timelines.
    & The {(link "Actors")}' goal is to steer the occurring chain of events to exist within the longest lasting instance of the universe.
    - {(bold "The Impossibilities")}: The entirety of all potential spacetime. The impossibilities stores the events banned from happening, compressing the possible events.
    - {(bold "The Possibilies")}: The possible spacetime storages the events allowed by {(link "mirrors" "determinism")}, condensing into the occuring.
    - {(bold "The Occuring")}: While it is not technically allowed to traverse between possible and occuring space, the {(link "Soies")} model allow to manipulate the possible space by forcing events to occur outside of the resolving spacetime.
    - {(bold "The Longest End")}, or {(ital "resolving spacetime")}: It is the surviving spacetime, its finality, the destination and meeting space of {(link "Actors")}.
SOIES MACHINE
  UNDE : Soies
  BREF : The {(link)} was the {(link "Feu" "last machine")}.
  BODY
    & The {(bold "Soies Machine")} is a kind of clock, with needles rotating around each available axis of space, at the fastest allowed speed by the {(link "Soies" "Occurence")}.
    & The purpose of the machine was to locate the required design across all timelines, forcing the {(link "Soies" "Occuring")} to render as the {(link "Longest End")}.
    & Sealed in an {(bold "Optimal Cartesian Vaccum")}, the clock spins inside a pocket of syntetic space ruled by optimal natural laws; an uttermost stable engineered universe, in a vaccum.
    & Each "needle" rotate in its own dimension, vanishing upon reaching the fatest renderable possibility — Effectively locating the {(bold "occurring")} within the possibles and impossible spaces.
SOIES INJECTION
  UNDE : Soies
  BREF : A {(link)} is a syntetic event found in the occurring.
  BODY
    & Injections are unnatural events found in the {(link "Soies" "Occurring")}, forced into existence by {(link "actors")} condensing the possible events.
    & The {(link "Andes Castel")} found in {(link "Laeisth")} is a known {(bold "injection")}, the {(link "Neon Hermetism" "Neon Hermetists")} suggest the {(link "Ehrivevnv")} to also be an injection.
NEAUSEA
  UNDE : Neon hermetism
  BREF : The {(link)} is a {(bold "sickness")} manifested in beings who knows their {(link "Soies" "Soies position")}.
  ICON : M60,150 L60,150 L240,150 M60,240 A90,-90 0 0,0 150,150 A90,90 0 0,0 240,240 M150,60 L150,60 L150,120
  BODY
    & {(link "Actors")} and beings such as {(link "Paradichlorisse")}, can carry it. A weaker form can be contracted when one is in contact with {(link "Nohlxeserre")} languages.
    & The experience of {(bold "Neausea")}, by the afflicted, would at first seem like one can travel through time. But the subject's impression of time-traveling is due to their focus shifting across possible sequences of events.
    & To the observer, the subject would simply collapse, by the time the body would hit the ground, the subject's mental gaze would have traveled across different possible timelines, but would have in the process {(ital "lost the track of Time")} — Effectively extracting themself from the {(link "Soies" "Occurring")}.
    & {(link "Andes")} is the only character known to have survived an encounter with the {(link "Nohlxeserre")} Languages. The fossilized mountains of corpses by the sides of {(link "Paradichlorisse")} are a testament of the ones who have tried to look at Time and perished.
    & {(ital "In debt are are my impossible selves, <br />for all the horrible days.")}
    λ (join host:children)
NOHLXESERRE
  UNDE : Neausea
  BREF : {(link)} is an hypothetical language from the {(link "Neauismetica")}.
  ICON : M60,150 L60,150 L240,150 M60,240 A90,-90 0 0,0 150,150 A90,90 0 0,0 240,240 M150,60 L150,60 L150,120
