  UNDE : Characters
  BREF : {(link)} is a being who periodically manifest itself on {(link "Laeisth")}.
  BODY
    & Rlionn is not a single individual but a trait that manifests itself as a collective state of mind for the inhabitant of the Oasis.
    & Spoken-of in tales and songs, the story of her children are sung in the album {(link "Children of bramble")} and illustrated in the {(link "Laeisth" "The Rlionn Oasis")} short.
NEONEV
  UNDE : Characters
  BREF : {(link)} is a daughter of {(link "Rlionn")}.
  BODY
    & While most of {(link "Rlionn")}'s Children do not stray far from the Oasis, one has left the desert of {(link "Laeisth")} to travel {(link "Dinaisth")}.
    & {(bold "Neonev")} has crossed {(link "Kanikule")} during the {(link "feu" "first season")}.
ANDES
  UNDE : Characters
  BREF : {(link)} immigrated through a {(link "Soies Injection")}.
  BODY
    & Shortly before the {(link "Feu" "first season")} and brought along tools to study the {(link "Ehrivevnv")}.
    & {(bold "Andes")} was already present on {(link "Dinaisth")} when {(link "Neonev")} and the other immigrants arrived, the role of Andes in the {(link "Yajnev" "Yajnev Collapse")} is unknown, but his arrival coincides with the destruction of {(link "Vetetrandes")}.
    & Prior to their arrival, a structure bearing their markings had been errected in {(link "Laeisth")}, known as the {(link "Andes Castel")}, suggesting an external manipulation of the {(link "Soies")}.
YAJNEV
  UNDE : Characters
  BREF : {(link)}'s {(ital "death")} engulfed {(link "Vetetrandes")} in an opaque impenetrable {(link "Ehrivevnv" "lock")}.
  BODY
    & Yajnev is a {(ital "Local-type")} {(link "Actors" "actor")}, meaning that its acting was mainly spacial, and only briefly temporal.
    & Its nervous imprint of local space could steer events locally, as well as affect time.
    & The space, and time, surrounding its body was animated by {(link "Yajnev")}'s reflexion and thoughts. The effect of the Immigrats approaching {(link "Dinaisth")} might have caused the collapse, as it may have had an effect similar to that of a foreign body injecting itself in the network of dimensional nerves.
PARADICHLORISSE
  UNDE : Characters
  BREF : {(link)} is a machine that speaks {(link "Nohlxeserre")}.
