  BODY
    - Find your passion and figure out how to {(bold "get paid for it")}.
    - Do whatever you want to do, but {(bold "be the best at it")}.
    - Strive for {(bold "simplicity and competence")}, but embrace the messiness along the way.
    - {(bold "Under-promise")} and over-deliver, and {(bold "own up")} to your screw-ups.
