    * Habits
    - Doing {(bold "the right tasks")} is more important than doing your tasks efficiently.
    - Write down your goals. {(bold "Break them down")} into manageable tasks.
    - Tackle {(bold "one task at a time")}, and group similar tasks together.
    - You're more attentive in the morning, tackle hard stuff then.
    - If you can't do it in 8 hours, you can't do it in 10.
    - Don't forget to stretch, and drink plenty of water.
    - {(bold "Keep a record")} of your time use.
    * Charisma
    - Always {(bold "look a person in the eye")} when you talk to them.
    - Always {(bold "stand up to shake someone's hand")}.
    - Be conscious of your {(bold "body language")}.
    - {(bold "Ask more")} than you answer.
    - {(bold "First impressions")} matter.
    - When you {(bold "walk, look straight ahead")}, not at your feet.
